rance, a French education and research organization. The actor claims to have leaked approximately 18,000 application records from the organization's 'toucan' subdomain as a 430 MB JSON file. We've logged 67 SUB-ZER0 incidents in our tracking, with 35 listed in the past week. #DataBreach #Education #ThreatIntelMore on this and other incidents → https://go.darkwebsonar.io/sub-zer0-mastodon", 'publication_date': 'Sun, 05 Jul 2026 17:17:27 +0000', 'source': 'https://infosec.exchange/@darkwebsonar/116868483895510053', 'source_type': "['']", 'source_level': 2, 'text': ["We tracked a data breach claim by SUB-ZER0 naming CampusFrance, a French education and research organization. The actor claims to have leaked approximately 18,000 application records from the organization's 'toucan' subdomain as a 430 MB JSON file. We've logged 67 SUB-ZER0 incidents in our tracking, with 35 listed in the past week.#DataBreach#Education#ThreatIntel"], 'observables': {'domain-name': ['go.darkwebsonar.io']}}, {'title': '🚨 NEWS: Data Breach e Notifica GDPR — Tempistiche, Procedure e Checklist Operativa per PMIEcco i punti chiave in breve: 💡 Il tuo server è stato violato. Un dipendente ha perso un laptop con i dati dei clienti. Un attacco ransomware ha crittografato il database. In quel momento, la priorità è fermare l’emergenza, ma il GD...🚀 LINK: https://meteoraweb.com/considerazioni-legali-ed-etiche/data-breach-e-notifica-gdpr-tempistiche-procedure-e-checklist-operativa-per-pmi?utm_source=mastodon&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=auto_share#dataBreach #incidentResponse #pMI #sicurezzaDati. #notificaGDPR', 'publication_date': 'Sun, 05 Jul 2026 15:16:47 +0000', 'source': 'https://mastodon.social/@meteoraweb/116867791283392644', 'source_type': "['']", 'source_level': 2, 'text': [], 'observables': {'domain-name': ['meteoraweb.com'], 'email-addr': ['meteoraweb@mastodon.social']}}, {'title': '“The IDRBT Domain Registration Portal (registrar.idrbt.ac.in) – the exclusive registrar for India’s .bank.in namespace – exposed its entire REST API via 33+ unauthenticated endpoints,” the post alleges. “Anyone with curl could retrieve the bcrypt password hashes, mobile numbers, email addresses, login IPs, and device fingerprints of all 5,576 bank employees trusted with managing India’s banking domains.”https://www.theregister.com/security/2026/06/30/indias-central-bank-mandated-use-of-bank-domains-to-enhance-trust-but-its-registry-leaked-sensitive-info/5264152#databreach #india #registrar #cybersecurity', 'publication_date': 'Sun, 05 Jul 2026 12:14:05 +0000', 'source': 'https://indieweb.social/@jbz/116867300994530341', 'source_type': "['']", 'source_level': 2, 'text': ['“The IDRBT Domain Registration Portal (registrar.idrbt.ac.in) – the exclusive registrar for India’s .bank.in namespace – exposed its entire REST API via 33+ unauthenticated endpoints,” the post alleges. “Anyone with curl could retrieve the bcrypt password hashes, mobile numbers, email addresses, login IPs, and device fingerprints of all 5,576 bank employees trusted with managing India’s banking domains.”'], 'observables': {'domain-name': ['bank.in', 'registrar.idrbt.ac.in', 'theregister.com'], 'email-addr': ['jbz@indieweb.social']}}]